      "rev": "rev3.0",
      "title": "Abandonment Program (rev3.0)",
      "steps": [
        "MIRU service rig and associated equipment.",
        "NU Class II 2M BOPE c/w Class A monitoring system on 8-5/8\" casing. Call for CalGEM inspection. (Assumed BHP ~1,293 psi; normally pressured at 0.43 psi/ft — top perf 3,443 ft MD = 3,007 ft TVD.)",
        "RIH tubing open-ended and attempt to reach TD at 3,793 ft.",
        "POOH.",
        "MIRU wireline and run CBL from 3,200 ft – 1,300 ft. Confirm ETOC with CalGEM.",
        "Call CalGEM to witness placing of cement.",
        "RIH open-ended tubing.",
        "Pump cement plug #1 from 3,793 ft – 3,097 ft (100 ft above top Ashton). ~170 cu ft Class G cement.",
        "WOC – tag plug at 3,097 ft (call CalGEM to witness).",
        "Pump cement plug #2 from 3,097 ft – 2,456 ft (100 ft above top UHZ). ~220 cu ft Class G cement.",
        "WOC – tag plug at 2,456 ft (call CalGEM to witness).",
        "Call CalGEM to witness placement of 72 lb/cu ft abandonment mud from 2,456 ft – 1,603 ft (292 cu ft).",
        "RIH open-ended tubing to 1,603 ft.",
        "Set balanced plug #3 from 1,603 ft – 1,394 ft (below base of USDW to 100 ft above BFW). ~72 cu ft Class G cement.",
        "Tag TOC at 1,394 ft or higher (call CalGEM to witness).",
        "Call CalGEM to witness placement of 72 lb/cu ft abandonment mud from 1,394 ft – 120 ft (436 cu ft).",
        "Set balanced plug #4 at 120 ft, cement to surface. ~42 cu ft Class G cement.",
        "Tag TOC (call CalGEM to witness).",
        "POOH.",
        "Confirm cement in all surface annuli.",
        "RDMO.",
        "Move in welder to cut casing 5–10 ft below grade; weld plate with well API # indicated.",
        "Call CalGEM to witness."
      ]
    },
